Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part A ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,父与母与面具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚军的机动堡垒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,躲进Armorzagan刚才埋伏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,后面坐好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的照做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？ 我的Gehennam被丢在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,本土的补给物资？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam由你驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没你的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆中尉没了武装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 有武器补给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,总监！ 您也来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}G G 贝鲁 贝鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam的舱门能开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人很难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的我也能！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁在驾驶 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 气色不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啾啾咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她喊他父亲…那就是亚美利亚军的总监？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是很大的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcane落进海里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我还没完全掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们救的你？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,您为什么来前线？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是贝鲁利·赛纳姆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我不会加入亚美利亚军的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会给你更换背包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,盖兹 驾驶Gehennam山上警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 在下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还不快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,总不能全指望Armorzagan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self出击前 我们会尽量抵挡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过Montero…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,干净的水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在技术人员看来那就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用G-Self的手操作外部控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没法在驾驶舱里操作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,接口匹配吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请尽快 贝鲁利·赛纳姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再退半步 好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利什么的 往前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好 最终形态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,光束和…导弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,装甲的闪光攻击和变色是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可以顺着脚边的缆绳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在下没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,狡诈背包朝后展开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈总监 拉莱雅拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁 步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那是狡诈背包的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里习惯吗 拉莱雅酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 艾达小姐请去保护自己的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,已经逐渐习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是飞得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,碍手碍脚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcane来护卫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一群苍蝇 别想绕到Armorzagan背后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉你现在才来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是单体飞行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,逃生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伯加斯被击落了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那架机动堡垒和机动战士配合！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那又是什么机体！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 空中格斗中起决定性作用的是高度！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在Elf·Bullock的机动性能面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看你能潇洒到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,必须重新拉升才能格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,背包朝前影响射击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,呼…有空气可以滑翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的水？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那是爆炸的闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁就在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,米克·杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,射击太不讲究了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,枪枪脱靶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉肯定又在抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,光束无法聚焦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知死活的烂铁皮！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,废铜烂铁给我滚远点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没有高度无法打赢空中格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意助我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有助推器的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拿下用不惯新背包的G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,绝非难事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没法保持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用心点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人还没收兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不去保护父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔方向有不明物体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不明物体？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有不明飞行物来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸乘坐的Belay上的摄像机捕捉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不用继续牵引仿真气球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fry-Schop也一起去掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不明飞行物…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达小姐 别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在胡闹什么 敌人在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,气球在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,到底想干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没能阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟只是气球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,气球？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,气球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这女孩 看起来不像有病啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,确定是Capital塔方向来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,映像分析
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是穿梭机尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 没有迎击的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达还不回来么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是「突击娘」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,克里姆中尉说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她是位敢于身先士卒的公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁 贝鲁 贝鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 贝鲁利·赛纳姆也在
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part B ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 明明没有空战能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,系统崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但只是暂时性的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哪里来的岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,米克·杰克 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见粉嘟嘟的G-Self放跑了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听得见吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,米诺夫斯基粒子已经很稀薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,背包的米诺夫斯基飞行平衡器…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 艾达小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,发什么毛病？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是艾达殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,米克 追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不看看机体都是什么状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达小姐在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,望远镜也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,尾翼的功率…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过载了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,比从Capital塔来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,高度还要高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去 我也可能回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雷达恢复了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self…正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不明飞行物也要从我下面溜过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不明飞行物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是大气层滑翔机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,从这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁 贝鲁 贝鲁 贝鲁利在哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一架滑翔机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等机体稳定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那种东西只要一枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以打！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就会捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,接住它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能起到刹车效果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 可是 可是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔的紧急逃生滑翔机能有什么威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点成了杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是贝鲁利·赛纳姆的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你真的是一个人开滑翔机来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来得匆忙 忘了给你买桂皮小松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为妈妈只记得冠艇时刻表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,事情变成这样 当妈的不可能不担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是海盗船的机动战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利·赛纳姆 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是 艾达·苏尔坎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,确认没有敌人 我们回Megafauna吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么Arcane飞这么高？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为了确认除滑翔机外没有其他敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长也去劝劝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那个年纪最不听大人话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那个年纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 放下放下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是冠艇的运营长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,运营长官叫韦米特·赛纳姆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利·赛纳姆是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在梅特巴尔国际会议上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,总监您一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这位莫非就是千金？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我叫艾达·苏尔坎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来时路上听贝鲁说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可别指望我为Capital塔上的事道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为我们的举动表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,近十年来我们的宇宙技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确实一度借鉴大陆战争的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,贡德梵的成功经验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 与荷米斯玫瑰设计图之类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没有丝毫的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,贵方有一艘宇宙战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,曾因触犯禁忌遭到SCord教声讨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\an7}SCord教：宇宙脐带教Space Umbilical cord，主张停止发展旧世纪科技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指那艘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已经停止建造的NicSpace号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘船已经被解体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,国际会议上也不曾有人提出问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果NicSpace是Megafauna的前身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么证据这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,船上有的部件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,刻着完全不同的厂商和生产日期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,将NicSpace改装为宇宙海盗船进行实战测试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,根据采集的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在亚美利亚本土陆续生产宇宙舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦明确来自宇宙的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,您所说的这些都算不上问题 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还要进行机体保养和维护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还不快去妈妈怀里喝奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,至少别用钢珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是亚美利亚拍摄的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是违禁么 观测天体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,月球周边有大量人工活动的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,「神轿」搬运光子电池的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就像宇宙本身的脉动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是「神轿」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其他几个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是近年来新出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为对抗月球周边出现的新的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,必须让宇宙世纪的技术得以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,SCord教之所以向地球分配光子电池
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了让地球上幸存的人类复兴家园
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔都应该是矗立不倒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁 诺蕾朵 我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拉莱雅也跟我回Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能够得到Capital军的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们愿意提供一架F-Rag
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那是长机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是面具上尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,预备兵员 清理散落在甲板的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不许漏掉一根螺钉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为只要来前线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就能得知卢因和诺蕾朵 贝鲁的下落…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,听说损失了半支编队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像昆达拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,昆达拉终究是昆达拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会把你的意见转告作战参谋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好 全体右转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拾到的东西全部放入回收箱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那是卢因·李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那群家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看见昆达拉失败高兴吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把我当作实验台…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是昆达拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这场败仗的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,必须以面具上尉的身份洗刷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,昆达拉也有自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我完成这份责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我支持你 上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卢因就是…面具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital军从贡德梵军借调了宇宙战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,否则那支部队不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,审讯我的昆珀·卢西达上校是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说调查部的昆珀上校？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他那样的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能不知道荷米斯玫瑰设计图的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,得告诉父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉总监去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一个人驾驶大气层滑翔机来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,打起点精神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔是重要的交通机构
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会被宇宙来的东西破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇大人明明说过…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== YOKOKU ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为了用Megafauna号返回大四叶草
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:06.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\an7}大四叶草：Big-Clover，Capital塔地面设施，分四大区域。\N{\alpha&HFF&}大四叶草：{\alpha}其中包括卫队培训所、冠艇运营局、宇宙脐带教大圣堂、圣芙兰学院等
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.06,0:24:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,必须尽量避开Capital军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是面具部队纠缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为多此一举
